Text: yeah!! I used not eat anything after 6pm because of school and then fast until the school ended the next day, around 2pm and not be hungry at all. with actively knowing I’m restricting I’m suddenly always hungry :(

Author: originalityshowingrn
Text: Me too! I restrict and have 400 calories for breakfast and lunch, but I try to reach 1500 to maintain, so I just want to eat everything in sight, because I “have too much calories left”. I’ve never had a full blown binge though, because I am scared of going over my limit...
